    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入玩家活动Q群：820137109（steam掌机、电竞椅等奖品）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入玩家交流Q群：704332191</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎加入测试Q群：168314512</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >咒语回声是一款单人游戏，将roguelike卡牌构建的战略深度与实时动态战斗的刺激相结合</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择合适的时机打出强力的咒语，遇到不同的事件，并在每场游戏中采用独特的策略来击败源源不断的敌人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/b8d4f4abb876380f86a0ccaf7704c314.avif?t=1750736224\" width=491 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/88bf48537d1871f2cce6b47b732adcb0.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主角会自动寻敌并攻击最近的敌人。只需选择合适的时机拖放并释放咒语 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/a181cfcb54e0655bf3d08e27c59cf2d2.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/038105a91ac78010ff9358394111b0fc.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每释放一次咒语都会增加你的热力值，热力值会随着时间的推移会逐渐减少<br>但当心了，过度释放咒语会进入过载状态，让你在完全冷却前不能释放任何咒语</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/f3d3830c702440a86dec242804ea41be.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/94cade7f010442b8d9fb2ca1d12e0563.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝藏、商店、面对精英怪物，或者探索未知，皆由你做主。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/928eb3f6a5d4cb146149a2566bae689d.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/e5a681afe4a75539207ddcc8a31c4c59.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将基础咒语融合成高阶咒语，或持有特定的多张咒语会触发额外的羁绊效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/6ea8cc6d7de7fe7f225c2df021cc0b98.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/305cd16d01e0caa120c2b10e65442ad9.webp?t=1750736224\" width=560 height=63 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+精心设计的咒语，50+独特的敌人，8个不同的英雄技能，还有多样的事件与圣物都在等你探索!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.poster.avif?t=1750736224\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.webm?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152290/extras/eabe4c5a5389eb2baafd5b9eb1a127c2.mp4?t=1750736224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
